# M1 demo screenshots land here

The chantier 05 demo script (`tools/scripts/demo-persistence.sh`) writes
PNGs to this directory at each scenario step. The `.gitignore` keeps
`*.png` out of the repo by default; this `.gitkeep` ensures the directory
itself is tracked so the script never has to mkdir.

Replace these placeholder docs with the actual capture flow once the
hardware (tablet + Windows mallette + screen-recording tool) is wired
up for the 4-May visio.
